Package com.gsm.model

Class PurchaseOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gsm.model.AuditableEntity
      • com.gsm.model.PurchaseOrder
  • @Entity
public class PurchaseOrder
extends AuditableEntity
    Represents the core Purchase Order (PO) entity. This class maps to the "PurchaseOrder" table and acts as the header for an order placed with a supplier for raw materials.
